<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,349,878,904]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Local names:</emphasis>
― 
<emphasis box="[377,441,879,905]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Sanin</emphasis>
(
<collectingRegion box="[455,534,878,904]" country="Papua New Guinea" name="Manus" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Manus</collectingRegion>
)
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[189,441,914,941]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="12.[136,1452,158,1301]" box="[189,441,914,941]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,253,914,940]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Uses:</emphasis>
―none recorded
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="12.[136,1452,158,1301]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,435,950,976]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Conservation status:</emphasis>
―Endangered. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Barfod &amp; Heatubun" authorityYear="2022" box="[609,815,950,976]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Licuala" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sandsiana">
<emphasis box="[609,815,950,976]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Licuala sandsiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has a restricted distribution. Deforestation due to logging concessions is a major threat in its distribution range.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="13" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="12.[136,1452,158,1301]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,328,1022,1048]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Etymology:</emphasis>
―Named after the collector of the 
<typeStatus box="[724,775,1023,1049]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">type</typeStatus>
, M.J.S. Sands, to pay tribute to his great contribution to our knowledge of the flora of New 
<collectingCountry box="[488,569,1058,1084]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Guinea</collectingCountry>
in general and Manus Island in particular.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
